# Database & Performance

## Query Optimization
- Favor `leftJoinLateral` for relational data (Product + Images) to avoid N+1 patterns.
- Group independent DB calls into `Promise.all` blocks.

## Schema Sync
- New indexes must be explicitly defined in `db/schema.ts` to align with PostgreSQL.
- **Port Gotcha:** Use port 5432 for `drizzle-kit push`. Port 6543 (pooler) will hang.